# MeteoSwiss MCP Server Documentation Guidelines

Always prioritize clear documentation for both humans and LLM agents:

1. Every module should include JSDoc comments for all exported functions, classes, and interfaces
2. Document parameter types, return types, and thrown exceptions
3. Include example usage where appropriate
4. Update relevant documentation when changing functionality

Reference our existing documentation structure when developing new features or making changes.
